snippet.title: Alien Scumbags Trailer (old)
snippet.description:
Run...Hide...KILL! Alien Scumbags is a 2D comedy horror shooter inspired by Doom and Duke Nukem, roam the darkness of the ship Nostrami but beware of the hell that awaits you.

Buy it now on PC here tinyurl.com/alienscumb

#indiedev #indiegame #horror #scifi
